Enum TileType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TileType>
      • TileType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TileType>

    public enum TileType
extends java.lang.Enum<TileType>
    An enum that specifies exactly what kind of tiles are used in the map. Allows for conversion from characters to actual loaded in images.
